e from the magnetization and $\\mu$SR data. Our\nSANS studies provide new insights into the nature of the inhomogeneities in a\nferromagnetic alloy close to a quantum critical point.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Thu, 28 Jul 2022 16:03:01 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Fri, 24 Feb 2023 16:18:01 GMT"}],"update_date":"2023-02-27"}
