s of 1.6ms/img and\n6.3ms/img, that is 8$\\times$ and 3$\\times$ faster than UNet and UNETR.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Fri, 29 Jul 2022 04:56:36 GMT"}],"update_date":"2022-08-01"}
