The property prediction errors of\npressure and equivalence ratio were remarkably lowered in spite of the low SNR\nattendant with reduced exposure.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Fri, 29 Jul 2022 05:33:32 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Mon, 12 Dec 2022 00:10:36 GMT"},{"version":"v3","created":"Mon, 26 Dec 2022 08:15:07 GMT"}],"update_date":"2023-01-02"}
